{"tid":2321325,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"炎亞綸5年前「下雨地震說」網朝聖　幽默回應：讓大家受驚","createTime":"2020-12-11T12:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T06:21:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef76d6680ccb4e5fb49b47f286698122da85386f","tid":2321325,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"台灣10日晚間21時19分東部海域發生有感地震，芮氏規模6.7，最大震度4級，堪稱是今年最大的地震，加上近期雨勢連綿不斷，讓許多網友憶起男星炎亞綸5年前的「下雨地震說」，紛紛湧入他5年前的貼文朝聖，而今日炎亞綸本人也在IG發限動做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/07/1629819-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F07%2F1629819-PH.jpg&h=510f95a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲昨日地震讓許多網友回憶起炎亞綸5年前的「下雨地震說」。（圖／翻攝自炎亞綸臉書）<br />\n<br />\n2015年炎亞綸在臉書上發文「好一陣子沒下雨，這週狂下雨，把原本乾燥的土壤一下淋濕，因此地質鬆軟造成今年的地震不斷。」而該篇文章在當時引起熱議，就有不少網友調侃「炎亞綸是地質系之父」，直到後來，有網友轉發一份來自英國南安普敦大學的研究，指出確實有下雨地震理論，不少網友看完報告紛紛向他道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/11/2929527-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F2929527-PH.jpg&h=f124d3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲炎亞綸PO出「下雨地震說」後發文道歉。（圖／翻攝自炎亞綸臉書）<br />\n<br />\n然而，10日的地震再度讓不少網友想起炎亞綸的「下雨地震說」，臉書粉絲專頁「台灣迷因taiwan meme」也立刻搭起風潮，在臉書PO出一道題，題目寫道「為什麼突然有這麼大的地震？」其中選項D就寫下「最近這幾天都在下雨」，並用炎亞綸和鬼滅之刃中的「炎柱」合成做成梗圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/11/2930501-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F2930501-PH.jpg&h=e207a3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲炎亞綸幽默回應。（圖／翻攝自aayan1120IG）<br />\n<br />\n炎亞綸今日就透過IG限時動態轉發，並用橘色字體幽默打下「最近都在練全集中呼吸～抱歉，讓大家受驚了」。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友也在梗圖底下留言，「炎柱大哥12/25發專輯摩登原始人是不是應該手刀去預購起來」、「D啊，下雨就地震」、「都過這麼久了還被拿出來鞭」、「炎之有理」、「炎柱根本先知好嗎」、「我炎柱大哥是對的」、「地質之呼吸」。"},{"pid":"931a18c12ac31955d8ca75cbafe04feb4c394edb","tid":2321325,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"Day能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207668ac33ae6ac7734d7b3412fbaf60ea041765","tid":2321325,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"931a18c12ac31955d8ca75cbafe04feb4c394edb","tid":2321325,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"Day能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:11:04.000Z","msg":"Day B<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b387c1daeebcc315d8b7c99691e81cd5eeaa81","tid":2321325,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f894fd854eb9a6ba44237561509b2d88184a50c","tid":2321325,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3b387c1daeebcc315d8b7c99691e81cd5eeaa81","tid":2321325,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"Geog界之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428da3724b4d83258acc0d05e57ef3968c650455","tid":2321325,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"居然成功爭取英國學府證明自己冇講大話🇬🇧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaf7684646a02573fe9be01c654e0949e6851ac","tid":2321325,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"